#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/07-file-systems.md:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Partitioning will allow the installation of several operating systems because it is impossible to have several of them cohabit on the same logical drive. Partitioning also allows the separation of data logically (security, access optimization, ...).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/07-file-systems.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "The division of the physical disk into partitioned volumes is recorded in the partition table, stored in the first sector of the disk (MBR: _Master Boot Record_).\n"
