msgid "*Extended partition*\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/07-file-systems.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "    There can be only one extended partition per physical disk, that is, a physical disk can have in the MBR partition table up to:\n"
